<section>
  <h1>Recording Studio Accessible</h1>
  <p>Optional access-control addon for RecordingStudio hosts.</p>

  <p>Integration mode: <strong><%= @integration_mode %></strong></p>

  <h2>What this addon provides</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><code>RecordingStudio::Access</code> and <code>RecordingStudio::AccessBoundary</code> recordables</li>
    <li><code>RecordingStudio::Services::AccessCheck</code> role lookup and authorization helpers</li>
    <li>Install and migration generators for host applications</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Dummy app access flow</h2>
  <dl>
    <dt>Workspace</dt>
    <dd><%= @workspace&.name || "Not seeded" %></dd>
    <dt>Root recording</dt>
    <dd><%= @root_recording&.id || "Missing" %></dd>
    <% @access_rows.each do |row| %>
      <dt><%= row[:label] %></dt>
      <dd>role=<%= row[:role] || "none" %>, allowed=<%= row[:allowed] %></dd>
    <% end %>
  </dl>

  <p>This route is optional and is not mounted by the installer unless the host app explicitly asks for it.</p>
</section>
